        {
          "key": "C",
          "text": "2k+1"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "2^(k-1)"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "B",
      "explanation": "At level k, there can be at most 2^k nodes (assuming level 0 is root).",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
